# Glossary

> Domain terms with definitions, invariants, and cross-references.
> AI agents retrieve domain context one term at a time — bounded
> scope per entry matters even within a single doc.

## Conventions

* One entry per term, alphabetical within sections.
* Lead each entry with a one-sentence definition.
* Invariants are declarative ("X is always Y") — not procedural.
* "Used in" lists modules, files, or other docs where the term
  appears, so agents can navigate to usage.
* "Related" links to other glossary entries for disambiguation.

